=== 評價 ===
{{RT prose|90|8.32|107||y|藉助朱妮·絲莫利特和強納森·梅爾斯的出色演出，米莎·葛林創作的《逃出絕命村》展現了洛夫克拉夫特創作的[[克蘇魯神話|克蘇魯神話]]中的驚悚元素，长老神不是宇宙之中唯一存在的神靈}}<ref name="RTS1">{{Cite rt |id=lovecraft_country |type=tv |season=1 |title=逃出絕命村 |accessdate=2020-10-21|language=en-US}}</ref>。」《逃出絕命村》第一季在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]網站上得到「普遍讚譽」，獲得了79/100分（42位劇評人）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/tv/lovecraft-country/season-1 |title=Lovecraft Country: Season 1 |website=Metacritic |accessdate=2020-10-21|language=en-US}}</ref>。

《[[影音俱樂部|影音俱樂部]]》的編輯香農·米勒（{{lang|en|Shannon Miller}}）稱讚劇集能夠平衡洛夫克拉夫特富有爭議的政治觀點與他「無與倫比的遠見卓識」之間的聯繫<ref>{{cite web |url=https://tv.avclub.com/lovecraft-country-is-a-stunning-horrific-look-at-a-gro-1844587271 |title=Lovecraft Country is a stunning, horrific look at a grotesque legacy |website=The A.V. Club |date=2020-08-07 |last=Miller |first=Shannon |access-date=2020-08-13 |dead-url=no|language=en-US}}</ref>。《[[泰晤士報|泰晤士報]]》的編輯雨果·里夫金德（{{lang|en|Hugo Rifkind}}）認為劇集充斥著野性和正義的憤怒<ref>{{cite web |last=Rifkind |first=Hugo |title=Lovecraft Country review: this is like nothing else — brutal and righteously furious |url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/lovecraft-country-review-this-is-like-nothing-else-brutal-and-righteously-furious-d9p3fmhhl |date=2020-08-21 |website=The Times |access-date=2020-08-24 |issn=0140-0460|language=en-GB}}</ref>。《[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]》的[[電影評論|影視評論家]]{{le|邁克爾·菲利普斯|Michael Phillips}}將劇集與此前不太成功的洛氏改編作品相對比，認為劇集在前人未曾探索的領域取得成功，同時稱讚劇集的主題<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/movies/michael-phillips/sc-ent-lovecraft-country-review-0807-20200806-so2cbobhkzcbxdgxmsei6rznyu-story.html |title=‘Lovecraft Country’ review: the wild side of ‘Green Book,’ pulled from the guts of American racism |website=Chicago Tribune |date=2020-08-07 |last=Phillips |first=Michael |access-date=2020-08-13 |dead-url=no|language=en-US}}</ref>。《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的編輯邁克·黑爾（{{lang|en|Mike Hale}}）表示節目統籌米莎·葛林擅長運用文化隱喻，將其出色地融入劇集之中<ref>{{Cite web|last=Hale|first=Mike|date=2020-08-13|title=‘Lovecraft Country’ Review: Nightmare on Jim Crow Street|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/13/arts/television/lovecraft-country-review.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-08-29|website=The New York Times|language=en-US}}</ref>。《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》雜誌的編輯丹尼爾·達達里奧（{{lang|en|Daniel D'Addario}}）評論道：「洛氏恐怖元素儘管極端暴力，但是仍然遜色於人類的邪念惡行<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2020/tv/reviews/lovecraft-country-review-1234727528/ |title=‘Lovecraft Country’ Uses Horror Traditions to Tell a Story of American Racism: TV Review |website=Variety |date=2020-08-07 |last=D'Addario |first=Daniel |access-date=2020-08-13 |dead-url=no|language=en-US}}</ref>。」

